headline.print_headline: White House Sets No Deadline for Russia on Ukraine
headline.main: White House Sets No Deadline for Russia on Ukraine

lead_paragraph: The White House says the U.S. government is still trying to determine who was responsible for Sunday's deadly shootout in eastern Ukraine and did not specify when Russia would have to meet the terms of a Geneva agreement for containing tensions in the former Soviet state.
